Interrupt-Based LED Control (AVR)

Description
An event-driven LED control system using external interrupt INT0 to change LED state instantly upon button press.

Tools & Libraries
- AVR Microcontroller  
- Atmel Studio  
- <avr/interrupt.h>, <util/delay.h>

Features
- External interrupt configuration (INT0)  
- Event-driven design (reduces CPU usage)  
- ISR implementation to toggle LED state  
- Real-time response to hardware events
